basic-files 0.1.0
Usage: basic-files [OPTIONS] <COMMAND> [ARGS]...

Commands:
  list      List syntax fixtures
  check     Check two-face coverage
  show      Show scopes for a file

Options:
  -c, --config <PATH>    Read fixture config
  -q, --quiet            Suppress summary output
  -h, --help             Print help
  -V, --version          Print version
